snippet: The teenager fell to his death in Crown Heights on Thursday when he tried to jump from one four-story apartment building to another, the police said.
abstract: Fifteen-year-old Tyreek Riley falls to his death in Crown Heights after trying to jump from top of one four-story apartment building to another.

byline.original: By LIAM STACK and REBECCA WHITE

lead_paragraph: The teenager fell to his death in Crown Heights on Thursday when he tried to jump from one four-story apartment building to another, the police said.

headline.main: Boy, 15, Dies Trying to Jump Between Rooftops in Brooklyn
